title: logins
body: i am aware of the fact that the servers are experiencing problems but, it says that the ranked queues were disabled but its not letting me login is that a part of their maintenance?

replies.body:
We had a live service incident last night just after 9:00pm PDT that was preventing logins. It was resolved shortly after it began, and was not part of the scheduled maintenance. 

Let me know if you have any questions.
oh, thank you for your relply
